      this method will be used to create the add root GUI and will call the methods required to add the root it will call the method handleAddRoot() method to create and add the root when the user enters the information and click on the add button of the Add root GUI the handleSelectItem() method is called here to enable selection of items on the tree

      this method is used to build the display info GUI and display the information of a selected item on the tree.

      this method will check which type of relatives is being added and add the new relative to the tree.
      void handleAddRoot(addRoot rootScene, javafx.stage.Stage stage)
      this method will handle the events when user click on the add button of the Add root GUI this method will get the information enter by the user and set the Personal and address information of the root person it create the root item and add the root to the familyTree the method buildFamilyTree() is called to build the tree

      this method will act like a reset button to allow user start a new tree this method is called when user click on create new tree This will reset the GUI back to the initial state

      void loadFamily(javafx.stage.Stage tempstage)
      this method is used to create the file chooser and handle the event of loading a family tree from selected file and build the familyTree .the method loadTree() is called to read the data from the file and then the buildFamilyTree() method is called to build the tree of the person loaded.This method is called when user click on load button.The file chooser will only filter .txt files
      void saveTree(javafx.stage.Stage tempstage)
      this method will create file chooser and handle the event of saving a tree to a file selected the method saveFamily() is called to use to write the family tree to the file selected.

    • Method Detail

      • CreatRoot

        public void CreatRoot()
        this method will be used to create the add root GUI and will call the methods required to add the root it will call the method handleAddRoot() method to create and add the root when the user enters the information and click on the add button of the Add root GUI the handleSelectItem() method is called here to enable selection of items on the tree

      • handleAddRoot

        public void handleAddRoot(addRoot rootScene,
                          javafx.stage.Stage stage)
        this method will handle the events when user click on the add button of the Add root GUI this method will get the information enter by the user and set the Personal and address information of the root person it create the root item and add the root to the familyTree the method buildFamilyTree() is called to build the tree
        Parameters:
        rootScene - the add root scene which will display the gui
        stage - the stage that holds the add root gui

      • handleSelectTreeItem

        public void handleSelectTreeItem()
        this methods handle the event when user click on a person of the tree if e.getClickCount is greater or equals to one means user click on an item if count is greater of equals to one ,the displayData() method is called to display the information of the item selected

      • displayData

        public void displayData(javafx.scene.control.TreeItem<FamilyMember> newValue)
        this method is used to build the display info GUI and display the information of a selected item on the tree. the edit details button will call the editDetails() method which will handle the event of editing a person details the add relatives button will call the addRelatives() method which will handle the event of adding a relative to a person
        Parameters:
        newValue - item selected by user
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException
        java.lang.ClassNotFoundException

      • addRelatives

        public void addRelatives()
        this method is used to create the add relatives GUI and will handle the event when user click the add button . The add Button will call the handleAddRelatives() method which will handle the event of adding the relative to the tree

      • handleAddRelatives

        public void handleAddRelatives(addRelative addRel,
                               javafx.stage.Stage stage)
        this method will check which type of relatives is being added and add the new relative to the tree.
        Parameters:
        addRel - the add relative GUI
        stage - the stage that holds the add relative GUI

      • editDetails

        public void editDetails(FamilyMember personSelected)
        this method is used to edit enable user to edit details of a selected button when the user click on the edit details Button .The save button will appear. the save button will handle the event to save the edited details by calling the method handleSaveNewDetails()
        Parameters:
        personSelected - the FamilyMember selected

      • handleSaveNewDetails

        public void handleSaveNewDetails(FamilyMember selected)
        this method will handle the event when user want to save the edited details
        Parameters:
        selected - familyMember selected by user

      • handleCreateNewTree

        public void handleCreateNewTree()
        this method will act like a reset button to allow user start a new tree this method is called when user click on create new tree This will reset the GUI back to the initial state

      • loadFamily

        public void loadFamily(javafx.stage.Stage tempstage)
        this method is used to create the file chooser and handle the event of loading a family tree from selected file and build the familyTree .the method loadTree() is called to read the data from the file and then the buildFamilyTree() method is called to build the tree of the person loaded.This method is called when user click on load button.The file chooser will only filter .txt files
        Parameters:
        tempstage - will hold the primary stage parameter

      • saveTree

        public void saveTree(javafx.stage.Stage tempstage)
        this method will create file chooser and handle the event of saving a tree to a file selected the method saveFamily() is called to use to write the family tree to the file selected. This method is called when user click on the save button
        Parameters:
        tempstage - primary stage
